{"tid":1994250,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"幫港出聲：黃絲騎劫「五一黃金周」封殺藍店　借「黃色經濟圈」分化港人 令香港撕裂達終極「攬炒」目標！","createTime":"2020-04-29T10:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T15:07:42.000Z","uid":2054,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1d1eb059fca6d75454dcdb2be4d8c5c12f263d","tid":1994250,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3PoTtUi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3PoTtUi.png&h=6c7c2d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020年04月28日 10:00<br />\n<br />\n香港社會撕裂，黃絲事事政治化，以政治凌駕一切。其後更有黃絲大搞「黃色經濟圈」，滲透政治消費主義。過往五一黃金周內地旅客平均每日約有百多個旅行團來港旅遊購物，但今年因應疫情影響下，內地來港人士須接受十四天隔離令而沒法到港消費，因此黃絲呼籲所謂「同路人」在黃金周只消費「黃店」，同時利用文宣曲解五一黃金周為「五大訴求，缺一不可」，誓要騎劫五一黃金周。發起人更指目前已招攬近千家商戶參與「黃色經濟圈」，同時要令「藍店」老闆遭受經濟打擊。<br />\n<br />\n以政治取向及目標為主而作出消費行為，打擊「藍店」商家，借「黃色經濟圈」繼續分化香港人，搞垮香港經濟，最終只會令香港撕裂，達到黃絲終極的「攬炒」目標！"},{"pid":"d1532da09f6d59bfe626b369d6dff8b171762fab","tid":1994250,"uid":274161,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"班藍絲除咗嬲嬲重可以做乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7dec77c6ef16673ebbcd01688fc4cec9cc9380","tid":1994250,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T10:44:46.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"434dc640f46772e63fa27bf12c031e117f924e6a","tid":1994250,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c072e48db1ef877cc32d6b0ef55d1637956f1c8","tid":1994250,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/